"{\"uid\": \"kbtx.com-2024-07-11-officers-take-part-annual-fundraiser-benefitting-special-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"BRYAN, Texas (KBTX) - Bryan and College Station law enforcement officers are participating in the annual Tip-a-Cop fundraiser.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 126, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7, \"end\": 12, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas\", \"score\": 0.9999928459869912, \"rank\": 6.454968653713088e-06, \"text\": \"Texas\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas\"}, {\"begin\": 14, \"end\": 18, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KBTX-TV\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"KBTX\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KBTX-TV\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KBTX-TV\"}, {\"begin\": 32, \"end\": 47, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kyle_Field\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9337827423674848e-14, \"text\": \"College Station\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kyle_Field\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kyle_Field\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The event raises money for the Special Olympics and its athletes.\", \"from\": 128, \"to\": 193, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 159, \"end\": 175, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.46171336398503e-19, \"text\": \"Special Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tip-a-Cop will be held from July 22 through 25 from 3 p.m. to 10 p.m.\", \"from\": 194, \"to\": 263, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 4-day fundraiser will see officers from multiple local agencies assisting wait staff for tips at the Texas Roadhouse - located at 1601 University Drive East.\", \"from\": 265, \"to\": 426, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The fundraising goal is $50,000.\", \"from\": 428, \"to\": 460, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Nationally, Tip-A-Cop is held only on July 25, however Lieutenant Jason James of the Bryan Police Department (BPD) said they stretched out the event because of its popularity.\", \"from\": 462, \"to\": 637, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 528, \"end\": 533, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jason\", \"score\": 0.6291006233620139, \"rank\": 0.48178636959212806, \"text\": \"Jason\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jason\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jason\"}, {\"begin\": 534, \"end\": 539, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_VI_and_I\", \"score\": 0.9689663823028829, \"rank\": 0.02818715864935601, \"text\": \"James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_VI_and_I\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_VI_and_I\"}, {\"begin\": 547, \"end\": 552, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Jennings_Bryan\", \"score\": 0.9994390307505985, \"rank\": 0.0003757307657766089, \"text\": \"Bryan\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Jennings_Bryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Jennings_Bryan\"}, {\"begin\": 553, \"end\": 570, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Police\", \"score\": 0.8421647585088993, \"rank\": 0.18642761769206018, \"text\": \"Police Department\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Police\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Police\"}, {\"begin\": 572, \"end\": 575, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston_Police_Department\", \"score\": 0.8704956957463402, \"rank\": 0.14877060454217086, \"text\": \"BPD\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston_Police_Department\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston_Police_Department\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have so many officers who want to participate, so much of the community want to come out to support the officers and the athletes,\\\" Lt. James said.\", \"from\": 639, \"to\": 790, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 779, \"end\": 784, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_VI_and_I\", \"score\": 0.9689663823028829, \"rank\": 0.02818715864935601, \"text\": \"James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_VI_and_I\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_VI_and_I\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lt. James also said this is an opportunity for law enforcement to interact with the community, and for the public to get to know the Brazos Valley officers.\", \"from\": 792, \"to\": 948, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 796, \"end\": 801, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_VI_and_I\", \"score\": 0.9689663823028829, \"rank\": 0.02818715864935601, \"text\": \"James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_VI_and_I\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_VI_and_I\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We just go out and have fun, and interact with the community,\\\" added Lt. James.\", \"from\": 950, \"to\": 1030, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1024, \"end\": 1029, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_VI_and_I\", \"score\": 0.9689663823028829, \"rank\": 0.02818715864935601, \"text\": \"James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_VI_and_I\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_VI_and_I\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This is a good time to talk to the officers, get to know the officers that patrol your area.\\\"\", \"from\": 1031, \"to\": 1125, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Acceptable donations include cash, checks, and credit card donations.\", \"from\": 1127, \"to\": 1196, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For more information, check out theirFacebookpage.\", \"from\": 1197, \"to\": 1247, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you are unable to make Tip-a-Cop and would like to make a monetary donation to the Special Olympics, you can goonlineor mail a donation to:  Bryan Police Department Lt. Jason James 303 East 29th Street Bryan, Texas 77803 979-209-5322 Checks payable to \\\"Special Olympics Texas.\\\"\", \"from\": 1249, \"to\": 1529, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1335, \"end\": 1351, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.46171336398503e-19, \"text\": \"Special Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1393, \"end\": 1398, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Jennings_Bryan\", \"score\": 0.9994390307505985, \"rank\": 0.0003757307657766089, \"text\": \"Bryan\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Jennings_Bryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Jennings_Bryan\"}, {\"begin\": 1399, \"end\": 1416, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Police\", \"score\": 0.8421647585088993, \"rank\": 0.18642761769206018, \"text\": \"Police Department\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Police\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Police\"}, {\"begin\": 1421, \"end\": 1426, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jason\", \"score\": 0.6291006233620139, \"rank\": 0.48178636959212806, \"text\": \"Jason\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jason\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jason\"}, {\"begin\": 1427, \"end\": 1432, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_VI_and_I\", \"score\": 0.9689663823028829, \"rank\": 0.02818715864935601, \"text\": \"James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q